      • flattenSortedByKey

        public static final int[] flattenSortedByKey​(com.carrotsearch.hppc.IntIntHashMap map)
        Converts an IntIntHashMap into a flat int [] array. The returned arrays contains [key,value] pairs and is sorted in ascending order by key values.

      • flatten

        public static final int[] flatten​(com.carrotsearch.hppc.IntIntHashMap map)
        Converts an IntIntHashMap into a flat int [] array. Even indexes in the flat array represent keys and the corresponding odd indexes -- values. Note: the order of keys in the flat array is arbitrary.
